{
  "stem": "25209.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was this river, river of, of people who wanted to escape.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there is a story to do with that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I'll let you ask a question.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Did you want to know more about Krakow?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When you were in Krakow, were there other refugees like you yourself?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there were, there was-- there were some Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They must have been friends of ours or something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Hm.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can remember a tall man who used to give me piggy backs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Doesn't help, does it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I have a feeling that we must have had a bit of a group there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How were they relating to me?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, just away from the Germans-- so I guess if you look at the map, they would be coming from the west.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were moving east.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Germans were moving east.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were moving east a few kilometers in front of them, hopefully.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The roads were chock-a-block full of people running with their little [INAUDIBLE], and bags, and kids.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the, the bombs were, were pretty scary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, you know, you got so used to the bombs, you, you heard a siren if you were lucky.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you ran.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in the middle, I do remember in the middle of the road-- I don't know, somewhere through, it must have been through the countryside-- these planes came really, really low and just machine gun-- gunned the people that were walking.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so we had the routine of running and, and just jumping into a ditch.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember this one particular time, we really had to-- like, they were just chasing.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
